# Instruqt + Git

This repository is the **Instruqt track** source (`paypal-elastic-serverless`).

## Always push to Instruqt

Whenever you **change track content** (challenges, `track.yml`, `config.yml`, `track_scripts/`, `docs/` used by the track, etc.), run **`instruqt track push`** (use `--force` if you normally do for this track) from the directory that contains **`track.yml`**, unless the user explicitly says not to. Do not end a session that edited the track without attempting this push.

Whenever you **commit and push to Git** (`git push`) for this project, also run **`instruqt track push`** from the same directory.

```bash
cd "$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)" && instruqt track push --force
```

If `instruqt track push` fails (auth, network), report the error and the exact command to run locally.

Track manager URL: https://play.instruqt.com/manage/elastic/tracks/paypal-elastic-serverless
